# Overview

The project goal is to make a personal site hosted on the internet. The three main components of this site are Hugo static site generator and wowchemy Academic template and GitHub hosting.

![maabedelhay.github.io](site.png)

The site home page contains my profile picture, biography, information about education, skills, experience and my posts.

## Hugo 
A static site generator takes your content, applies it to a template, and generates an HTML based static site. Itâ€™s excellent for blogs and landing pages.

- Benefits:

   - Quick deployment
   - Secure (no dynamic content)
   - Fast load times
   - Simple usage
   - Version control

To start with Hugo first i downloaded the [last version](https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases) of Hugo. Then i created a new repository cloned from Wowchemy academic template. After cloning the repository and creating a new repository to host the site. I generated the site using Hugo. 

## Wowchemy

The Wowchemy Hugo academic template help to create  the site and supply the neded file to us so we can customize it and work on it.

![s](wowchemy.png)

Simply cloned the [template](https://github.com/maabedelhay/starter-hugo-academic) as a new repository.

## Github

GitHub free hosting is the main allowed us to host the site on the internet. by creating a repository in the form of username.github.io. In this repository the coded of the site.

![s](github-io.png)

